                            The Stranger and the Secretary
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/canon-hub">Canon Hub</a> &raquo; <a href="/the-man-who-wasnt-there-hub">The Man Who Wasn't There Hub</a> &raquo; The Stranger and the Secretary
